featured_reviews.review_id: Located in the heart of Old Delhi, Jama Masjid is the largest and most well-known mosque in India. It was constructed between 1650 and 1656 under the reign of Mughal emperor Shah Jahan and it took more than 5000 labourers to complete this extravagant structure. Built in red sandstone and marble, this revered mosque has three gates, fours towers, two 40-metre high minarets and a courtyard that can hold 25,000 devotees. Please note that entry is not allowed in the mosque during prayers.
featured_reviews.review_text: Located in the heart of Old Delhi, Jama Masjid is the largest and most well-known mosque in India. It was constructed between 1650 and 1656 under the reign of Mughal emperor Shah Jahan and it took more than 5000 labourers to complete this extravagant structure. Built in red sandstone and marble, this revered mosque has three gates, fours towers, two 40-metre high minarets and a courtyard that can hold 25,000 devotees. Please note that entry is not allowed in the mosque during prayers.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
*_Madrasah Hanfiyah Warat Al-Ulum_*
*_Madrasa Hanafia Warisul Uloom_*

*Dajjal*
,

*_Dajjal will appear approximately 6 or 7 years after the appearance of Hazrat Imam Mehndi Raziallahu Taala Anhu. He will be a person from the community of Jews. His title among the people will be Messiah. His right eye will be hanging outside like a grape. His hair will be curly and he will ride very fast. He will have a big donkey written on his forehead q  f r Kafir which every uneducated Muslim will be able to read, along with him there will be an army of 70,000 people of Jews who will pledge allegiance to him, along with him will be a huge fire which will be named Jahannam but in reality it will be There will be heaven and a very big garden which will be named Jannat but it will be hell, it will roam around with it, it will claim its ownership, whoever calls it God will go to heaven and whoever doesn't agree will put him in hell, it will patrol the entire world only 40 He will remain in this world only for one day, but his first day will be equal to 1 year, second day will be equal to 1 month, third day will be equal to 1 week and the remaining 37 days will be equal to normal days_*

*_ When Sahabah Ikram Raziallahu Taala Anhu came to know about this, everyone asked Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam that O Messenger of Allah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, in those days when 1 day will be equal to 1 year, then how will Namaz be offered, then you say that by guessing. Will have to study for the whole year_*

*_He will try to go to Mecca and Medina by committing murders all over the world, but some angels of Allah will be guarding that border with naked swords so that he will not be able to enter inside_*

*_When it appears, there would have been a famine in the world two years before that and there would have been a severe shortage of grains, then it would miraculously produce grains, plant fruits on trees, and make the animals fat so that they would start giving plenty of milk. Will raise the dead_*

*_In that year, there will be 3 major earthquakes in Arab Sharif and those whose faith is weak will come out of the city and will join the community of Dajjal. At the same time, there will be an old man in Madinah Tayyabah who will come out to question Dajjal when he will face Dajjal. If you are presented in front of Dajjal, then on seeing him, he will say that I have recognized you, you are the one about whom our Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam had given us the news long ago, Dajjal will be very surprised to hear that you are unclean and will put a saw on his head and cut him into two pieces. He will tear it into pieces and then he will say to his followers that should I not bring him back to life again so that your faith becomes stronger and then he will join both the pieces and by the power of Allah he will come back to life as soon as he comes back to life? Then he will say that now my faith has become stronger than before that you are defiled, then he will get angry and try to kill them but this time he will not be able to kill them and in the end he will put them in his hell which is from Allah. After this there will be heaven, it will not be able to show any wonder, then from there it will disappear and leave for the country in the evening_*

*_On the other hand, Imam Mehndi Raziallahu Taala Anhu will be busy preparing for the fight with him that as soon as the time for Asr Namaz will be ready, at the same time Hazrat Isa Alaihissalam will descend on the minaret of the mosque sitting on the arms of angels and will call out to bring the ladder. Then he will be brought down from there, Hazrat Imam Mehndi (Raziallahu Ta'ala Anhu) will ask Hazrat Isa for Imamat but if you say no, then Hazrat Imam Mehdi (Raziallahu Ta'ala Anhu) will offer Imamat and Hazrat Isa (Alaihis Salaam) will be appointed.

*_Then when Imam Mehndi Raziallahu Taala Anhu will hand over the command of the army to Hazrat Isa Alaihissalam, then Hazrat Isa Alaihissalam will say that you should command the army, I have come only to kill Dajjal and Hazrat Isa Alaihissalam will go after Dajjal at that time in your breath. This effect will be that it will go for many kilometers and anyone who comes under its control will melt like salt in water. You will chase Dajjal and take him to Baba 'Lad' and kill him quickly so that he does not melt and his blood. We will show it to our people so that the Muslims get relief and the Muslims will be engaged in eliminating his army to the extent that if a Jew is hiding behind a stone or a tree, then that stone and the tree will call out, O noble servant of Allah, an infidel is hiding behind me. Come and kill him_*

*_In this way, after the killing of Dajjal, the reign of Hazrat Imam Mehndi (Radiyallahu Ta'ala Anhu) will be established over the entire earth_*

* Jalzalatus Saat, Safah 7*
*Anwarul Hadith, page 135*
